Homefront is a weekly radio show hosted by Danny Lipford, best known for his appearances on The Weather Channel[1], and is co-hosted by Allen Lyle. Homefront shares expert advice and information about a variety of home topics. Many questions from listeners are answered during the show. The show airs on Saturdays from 10-12pm est.[2]
